</lg>
<lg n="3" met="anuṣṭubh">
<l n="a"><lb n="3"/>deva-bhūyaṅ gatasyāpi<space/>n</l>
<l n="b">pituś śrī-vīravarmmaṇaḥ <space/></l>
<l n="c">nāmasmr̥tyai vr̥ṣam imaṁ <space/></l>
<l n="d">śilāmayam atiṣṭhipat·</l>
